name: Vincenzo
overview: During a visit to his motherland, a Korean-Italian mafia lawyer gives an unrivaled conglomerate a taste of its own medicine with a side of justice.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: During a visit to his motherland, a Korean-Italian mafia lawyer gives an unrivaled conglomerate a taste of its own medicine with a side of justice.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Vincenzo Cassano's homecoming is met by distrusting tenants and eager fraudsters. Hong Yu-chan relinquishes his parental rights to Hong Cha-young.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Warned about a scheduled demolition of Geumga Plaza, Vincenzo contrives to thwart the attack. Yu-chan receives a call from a whistleblower.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Vincenzo warns an impassioned Yu-chan about the dangers of a new drug and its even more harmful pharmaceutical company. Choi Myung-hee shows her claws.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Fighting fire with fire, Yu-chan's supporters unite their efforts to carry out his vision of justice. Vincenzo employs Myung-hee's tactics against her.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Jang Joon-woo reminds Jang Han-seo who's the boss. The tenants rally around Vincenzo and Cha-young, who team up to take down Babel Group.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Both sides use every trick in the book to cause disturbances in and out of the courtroom. Han Seung-hyuk and Myung-hee are introduced to Babel's CEO.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Stumped by surprise witnesses, Joon-woo and Myung-hee direct their rage toward Cha-young. The tenants gain new appreciation for their building.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Angered by another conglomerate and its generations of unpunished crimes, Vincenzo tries to charm a young bank president out of investing in Babel.

guest_stars.character: Hwang Min Sung [CEO of Shinkwang Bank]
guest_stars.name: Kim Sung-cheol

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Joon-woo wields his power to force loyalty from his partners. Cha-young finds refuge in Vincenzo's apartment following a break-in.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Seeking revenge instead of liability for the loss of more innocent victims, Vincenzo puts his life on the line to lure Babel's CEO out of hiding.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: The search for Jang Han-seok begins with torturing his lackeys for information. An Gi-seok flashes his work badge to free Vincenzo from prosecution.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Han-seo faces unintended consequences when he takes a shot at Babel's throne. Vincenzo and Cho Ju-yeong finally get Geumga Plaza to themselves.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Ju-yeong reveals his true motive. As incoming CEO, Han-seok is met with admiration, applause and a mafia-styled surprise from Vincenzo.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: To expose Han-seok’s paper company, Vincenzo and Cha-young go undercover as an enamored couple. Seo Mi-ri reveals her high-tech tricks.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: With ample evidence to lock up Han-seok, Jung In-kuk holds a press conference. Vincenzo channels spirits to turn an ill-famed newspaper against Babel.

guest_stars.character: Oh Jung Bae [CEO of Daechang Daily]
guest_stars.name: Jeon Jin-gi

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Maddened by Vincenzo's ability to slip out of another one of his bloody traps, Han-seok goes after what Vincenzo cherishes the most.

guest_stars.character: Oh Jung Bae [CEO of Daechang Daily]
guest_stars.name: Jeon Jin-gi

episodes.name: Episode 17
episodes.overview: A grieving Vincenzo crashes a party to bleed Babel Group dry of its powerful allies. Seung-hyuk reaches out to a high-level commander for help.

episodes.name: Episode 18
episodes.overview: Fearing for his life, Han-seok goes to jail to bide some time. A visitor from Italy tells Vincenzo his help is urgently needed back home.

episodes.name: Episode 19
episodes.overview: Vincenzo and Cha-young present damning evidence against Babel Tower and its influential cronies. Myung-hee proves her loyalty toward Han-seok.

episodes.name: Episode 20
episodes.overview: Han-seok lets nothing stand in his way of revenge. Seeking justice the mafia way, Vincenzo gives his enemies a slow and painful death.

guest_stars.character: Hwang Min Sung [CEO of Shinkwang Bank]
guest_stars.name: Kim Sung-cheol
